{"tid":2306164,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE 新專輯曲目表曝光　金采源參與作詞作曲！","createTime":"2020-11-30T09:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T16:04:18.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"135e56d236940aebd4fc8405e291c62b74ec72ae","tid":2306164,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T09:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_31e5cde7270e6e33d07b0d6cd5f13890/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-30/131990-886960.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_31e5cde7270e6e33d07b0d6cd5f13890%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-30%2F131990-886960.png&h=7f6f297d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每次發片有精巧概念設定的 IZ*ONE，這次也以多首新歌詮釋電影主題，其中還有成員參與創作的作品！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOff the Record 今天（30 日）公開了 IZ*ONE 第四張迷你專輯〈One-reeler / Act IV〉的完整曲目表，以最新主打歌 &ldquo;Panorama&rdquo; 為首，將收錄 &ldquo;Mise-en-Scene&rdquo;、&ldquo;Island&rdquo;、&ldquo;Sequence&rdquo;、&ldquo;O Sole Mio&rdquo; 和「慢旅」共六首歌。<br />\n<br />\n特別的是，成員金采源這次在繁忙的行程內仍接下新挑戰，為最後一首歌「慢旅」參與了作詞、作曲工作，令歌迷更期待這張新專輯。<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE 將於 12 月 7 日發行〈One-reeler / Act IV〉，最近也別忘了鎖定更多的預告囉！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0ee4d09acb44cd1bd6dbb4571c30e4c5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-30/131990-886959.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0ee4d09acb44cd1bd6dbb4571c30e4c5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-30%2F131990-886959.jpeg&h=655248d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d6448f540d1d4dc42d553980e0dc7c32/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-30/131990-886961.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d6448f540d1d4dc42d553980e0dc7c32%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-30%2F131990-886961.jpeg&h=7b8aef66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87744042ac01f46521ec2fc98557d46f9182782f","tid":2306164,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep